# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...
#
# Set this to your DeepSeek API key when you want /api/questions/extract and
# /api/attempts/:id/llm-score to call the real model. When the variable is
# absent, those routes return LLM_NOT_CONFIGURED 400 and the manual paste
# routes (/api/questions/import, /api/attempts/:id/score) keep working.
#
# Never commit a real key. This file is the example template only.
